Goldstein, Respondent, v. Stern, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. May 5, 1890.) Appeal from city court of New York, general term.

Argued before Larremore, 0. J., and Bookstaver, J.

S. F. Hyman, for appellant. M. E. Goodhart, for respondent.

No opinion. Appeal dismissed, with costs. See ante, 74.
